    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You designate a creature within range and convert its blood into virulent acid. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, it takes 10d12 acid damage and is stunned by the pain for 1d4 rounds. On a successful save, it takes half the damage and isnâ€™t stunned.<br>Creatures without blood, such as constructs and plants, are not affected by this spell. If blood to acid is cast on a creature composed mainly of blood, such as a @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl-bf.koboldpressmonsters.Actor.KPbloodelemental]{blood elemental} or a @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl-bf.koboldpressmonsters.Actor.KPbloodzombie000]{blood zombie}, the creature is slain by the spell if its saving throw fails.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl-bf.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
